<architecture>
- Droptidy runs on micro‑services in Docker.
- Backend: Python 3.12 + FastAPI.
- Frontend: Next.js 14.
</architecture>

<naming>
- Files and functions: snake_case.
- Classes: PascalCase.
- Test files: *_test.py.
</naming>

<api>
- Base URL: https://api.droptidy.ai/v1
- Use plural paths: /files, /jobs.
- Each response is JSON with a "data" key.
</api>

<abbreviations>
- FNS = File Normalization Service
- CLS = Cleaning Logic Service
- UDL = User Data Layer
</abbreviations>